lines.text: Shauna, we gotta stay together. We stay together, we stay safe.
Yeah, that's what they said in Jonestown.
You can't just go in there. You don't even know what it is.
What's the worst it could be?
I don't know. It could, like, be the Gates to Hell or something.
Yeah, like a hole in the ground that leads right to Satan.
You're thinking about a singles bar.
